OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,6,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FTurning brighter with sunny spells and
OL,8,Fshowers in the afternoon, some likely
OL,9,Fheavy and thundery.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers will clear this
OL,12,Fevening. Overnight it will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome clear spells inland, while
OL,14,Fcoastal areas will see mist or fog
OL,15,Fpatches and risk of light drizzle.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FMainly dry and settled with
OL,18,Flight winds. Cloudy at first with
OL,19,Frather damp and murky conditions near
OL,20,Fcoasts, but soon brightening up with
OL,21,Fgood spells of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
