OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled conditions prevailing,
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine for most. Some
OL,8,Fpatchy cloud may linger around the
OL,9,Fcoast at times in the mornings.
OL,10,FFeeling warm, but chillier on coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
